# Calibration profiles — only the current *operating* profile is tracked
# (§10 firmware<->ML contract). delaycal writes candidates here routinely and
# superseded locks are kept locally, so the directory is ignored by default:
# locking a new operating profile is a deliberate act, so add it explicitly
# (git add -f) and update this exception.
